_sText: This is the final version for the map Ishar 2. Inspired in one abandonaware game called Ishar 2: Messenger of Doom. This map works only with GarrysMod and CSS. This map is a test that mixed Irvan's Island and Zach's Island in one small map. The target is to do finally those islands individually. This is the final version, as there is another one in garrysmod.org with the same name that is alpha. Extract in : C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\user\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
